# Privacy Policy

## Introduction
NeuNo ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect any information when using our app.

## Data Collection
- Our app does not collect personal data.
- The app fetches public beamline status data but does not store or share any user information.

## Notifications
- The app sends notifications based on beamline status changes.
- Users can enable or disable notifications in their device settings.

## Third-Party Services
- Our app may access third-party beamline data but does not modify or redistribute it.
- No personally identifiable information is shared with third parties.

## Security
We prioritize security and use Apple's built-in privacy protections.

## Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at xingj@ornl.gov.

